Nim Di Chhavein - Theater Play
ABOUT PLAY
Nim Di Chhavein is based on a tragic love story of Bala & Taajo. It revolves around the struggle of love when economical circumstances hit the middle class.
Writer: Safdar Meer
Director: Faiz Rasool
Art Direction & Producer: Faizan Rasheed
Music Direction & Sound Design: Haider Zaidi
Video Direction: Hassan Amin
